Amazon Augmented AI (Amazon A2I) provides built-in human review workflows for common machine learning use cases, such as content moderation and text extraction from documents. 


Amazon Textract
	-	It is a machine learning service that automatically extracts text and data from scanned documents.With Amazon A2I, you can also create your own workflows for machine learning models built on Amazon SageMaker or any other tools.
 
 
Amazon Lightsail 

	-	Is a Virtual Private Server (VPS) provider, which offers a variety of templates to choose from. For anyone who is looking to host their applications on the Cloud, Amazon Lightsail is one of the easiest ways to get started for developers, small businesses, students, and other users.
 

AWS OpsHub

AWS OpsHub is a graphical user interface you can use to manage your AWS Snowball devices, enabling you to rapidly deploy edge computing workloads and simplify data migration to the cloud. 
